  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, whisk together soy sauce, olive oil, garlic, cumin, paprika, chili flakes, and lemon juice.",
    "3. Add the tofu cubes and chopped onion to the marinade. Mix well to coat.",
    "4. Thread the marinated tofu and onion onto skewers.",
    "5. Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until the tofu is golden brown and the onion is tender.",
    "6. Serve hot with additional lemon wedges, if desired."
